      "role": "user",
      "content": "wow thats a really intense start lol. it sounds like you're already really leaning into it. can u help me expand on the part about meritocracy? like i need to address the counter-argument that people should just work hard for what they earn, but i want to frame it in a way that shows why that idea is kind of a myth in this context. how would u write that part to make the meritocracy argument look weak?",
